# API conventions (data layer)

Project hub: repository root `AGENTS.md`. Use `api-core` for app/auth context and `api-http` when routes or services must align with repository changes.

# API Database Patterns

## Database Architecture

The API uses **PostgreSQL** with **SQLAlchemy ORM** for database operations.

### Connection Management

Database connections are managed through SQLAlchemy engine and session factories:

```python
from sqlalchemy import create_engine
from sqlalchemy.orm import sessionmaker

# PostgreSQL connection
POSTGRES_URL = f"postgresql://{user}:{password}@{host}:{port}/{db}"

# Engine with optimized settings
engine = create_engine(
    POSTGRES_URL,
    echo=bool(os.getenv("SQL_ECHO", "false").lower() == "true"),
    pool_size=int(os.getenv("DB_POOL_SIZE", "20")),
    max_overflow=int(os.getenv("DB_MAX_OVERFLOW", "40")),
    pool_pre_ping=True,      # Verify connections before use
    pool_recycle=3600,       # Recycle connections every hour
    pool_timeout=30,         # Wait up to 30s for connection
    connect_args={
        "connect_timeout": 10,
        "options": "-c statement_timeout=300000"  # 5 min query timeout
    }
)

# Standard session factory
SessionLocal = sessionmaker(autocommit=False, autoflush=False, bind=engine)

# Batch session factory (optimized for bulk operations)
BatchSessionLocal = sessionmaker(
    autocommit=False,
    autoflush=False,
    bind=engine,
    expire_on_commit=False  # Keep objects accessible after commit
)
```

## SQLAlchemy Models

### Core Model Pattern

```python
from sqlalchemy import Column, String, DateTime, Boolean, ForeignKey, Text, ARRAY
from sqlalchemy.dialects.postgresql import UUID, INET, JSONB
from sqlalchemy.orm import relationship
from sqlalchemy.ext.declarative import declarative_base
from datetime import datetime
import uuid

Base = declarative_base()

class Program(Base):
    """Bug bounty programs - central entity for scoping assets"""
    __tablename__ = "programs"
    
    # Primary key (UUID)
    id = Column(UUID(as_uuid=True), primary_key=True, default=uuid.uuid4)
    
    # Required fields
    name = Column(String(255), unique=True, nullable=False, index=True)
    
    # Array fields
    domain_regex = Column(ARRAY(Text), default=[])      # Regex patterns for scope
    out_of_scope_regex = Column(ARRAY(Text), default=[]) # Exclusion patterns
    cidr_list = Column(ARRAY(Text), default=[])         # CIDR ranges
    safe_registrar = Column(ARRAY(Text), default=[])    # Trusted registrars
    
    # JSONB for flexible data
    notification_settings = Column(JSONB, default=dict)
    
    # Optional fields
    phishlabs_api_key = Column(String(255), nullable=True)
    recordedfuture_api_key = Column(String(255), nullable=True)
    
    # Timestamps
    created_at = Column(DateTime, default=datetime.utcnow, nullable=False)
    updated_at = Column(DateTime, default=datetime.utcnow, onupdate=datetime.utcnow, nullable=False)
    
    # Relationships
    apex_domains = relationship("ApexDomain", back_populates="program", cascade="all, delete-orphan")
    subdomains = relationship("Subdomain", back_populates="program", cascade="all, delete-orphan")
    ips = relationship("IP", back_populates="program", cascade="all, delete-orphan")
    # ... more relationships
```

